INSERT INTO `content_props` VALUES ('58', '<h1 class=\"heading\">Our Team</h1>\r\n<p>By operating Spirit Asia Travel as a local travel company in South-East Asia, we’re able to provide our travellers with better support and overall experiences. Our ground teams are passionate about their regions and want you to take home incredible memories of their country. They’ll give you a deeply local knowledge as well as the reassurance of knowing they’re on hand to ensure your adventure runs smoothly and professional.</p>\r\n<p>An incredible trip doesn\'t just come from the itinerary - it\'s our trip leaders/guides who deserve most of the credit. Without them, you would barely scratch beneath the surface of a destination! Our clients frequently tell us that having an Spirit Asia Travel guide feels like a friend showing you around their country, introducing you to their culture, civilization and revealing the local hot spots. But our guides offer more than just insider knowledge. Having passed our rigorous training courses and they are masters of organisation and logistics, who have experienced almost any situation that comes up while travelling. Whether it\'s a local showing you around their country, or an impassioned ex-pat who loves adventure travel, your Spirit Asia Travel local leaders/guides will make sure your trip is unforgettable for all the right reasons.</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re worrying about whether or not you\'ll fit in with your group, don\'t panic, as we\'re fairly sure you\'ll at least have the essential qualities in common: a yearning to discover new things about a corner of the world, a sense of adventure and a desire to get out and mingle with the locals. </p>\r\n<p>Leave your footprint and take your memory…</p>\r\n<table class=\"founder\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h2>Vireak – Founder / Director</h2>\r\n<p>Company founder Vireak Soung has a long association with Tourism. Starting as a Cambodia Tour Operator in 1997, he has now worked for many international travel companies throughout Indochina (Cambodia, Vietnam, Laos). As a seasoned Tour Operator, Vireak started Spirit Asia Travel in 2007 to run the tours that he wanted to operate, in many different Spirit Styles of travel. Vireak lives for travel. Taking on most responsibilities at Spirit Asia Travel (SAT), sees Vireak spending half of his time in the office arranging Trips, and the other half - on Tour! If you have any contact with Spirit Asia Travel, chances are you\'ll come across Vireak.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"250\"><img src=\"uploads/images/vireak.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"212\" /> </td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h2>Vireak – Founder / Director</h2>\r\n<p>Company founder Vireak Soung has a long association with Tourism. Starting as a Cambodia Tour Operator in 1997, he has now worked for many international travel companies throughout Indochina (Cambodia, Vietnam, Laos). As a seasoned Tour Operator, Vireak started Spirit Asia Travel in 2007 to run the tours that he wanted to operate, in many different Spirit Styles of travel. Vireak lives for travel. Taking on most responsibilities at Spirit Asia Travel (SAT), sees Vireak spending half of his time in the office arranging Trips, and the other half - on Tour! If you have any contact with Spirit Asia Travel, chances are you\'ll come across Vireak.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"uploads/images/vireak.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"212\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', null);
